main event: A report from Project Blue Book detailing a sighting of unidentified flying objects near Green Bay, Wisconsin on August 25, 1955.
interesting points: The sighting lasted between 10 to 30 seconds,The observed objects were described as having a cigar shape and were approximately the size of a P-47,The observer initially thought the objects were parachutes but later retracted that statement,Investigation indicated that the sighting may have been a hoax,The report mentions that the observer had been under a doctor's care prior to the sighting.
witness description: serviceman for National Cash Register Company, age 26
